# ── Pipeline artifacts (regenerable) ─────────────────────────────────────
# Cache dir holds all parquet outputs (prices, walk-forward, regime, forecast,
# nav, trades, risk_events) plus the generated MD reports. Bump
# `cache_dir` in your PipelineConfig if you want a different location.
cache/
benchmarks/

# Generated reports at the project root (CLI writes inside cache/ by default,
# but a custom --cache-dir might land them anywhere — these patterns are a
# safety net so a stray run doesn't accidentally commit a 50-MB equity curve).
/report_*.md
/eval_report_*.md
/nav_*.parquet
/trades_*.parquet
/risk_events_*.parquet
/regimes_*.parquet
/forecasts_*.parquet
/prices_*.parquet
/wf_*.parquet

# ── Secrets ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.local
*.pem
*.key

